General.Name: SMO ClinPlus Co. Ltd.
General.Description: SMO ClinPlus CO.,LTD. provides site management services in research development in pharmaceuticals, medical devices, and health-related products in China. The company's SMO services incudes preliminary model establishment, preliminary plan preparation, initiation of clinical trial sites, on-site implementation, and project management services. SMO ClinPlus CO.,LTD. was founded in 2009 and is based in Shanghai, China.
